get.summary: Gets customer number for the customer using the email id
Gets verification data for the registered customers

put.summary: Updates verification details of the specified customer

get.summary: Gets profile data for the registered customer

put.summary: Updates profile information of the specified customer

get.summary: Gets alerts for the registered customer
Gets alerts for the registered customer

post.summary: Inserts new records for alerts for the specified customer

put.summary: Updates records for alertid specified in the request body. If alert does not exists, service ignores the alertid. Does not require path parameter

get.summary: Gets document list for the registered customer
Gets document metadata for the specified document id
Gets document in the form of PDF for the registered customer

post.summary: Creates transaction records for the specified customer

get.summary: Gets list of estimates and their data for the specified customer
Gets file (pdf/html) for the specified estimate

parameters.name: moveid
parameters.description: id of the move with status as estimate

put.summary: Updates estimate information for the specified estimate (move) id

parameters.name: moveid
parameters.description: id of the move with status as estimate

get.summary: Gets full data for the specified move

put.summary: Updates move information for the specified move id

parameters.name: moveid
parameters.description: id of the move with status as Pending, Booked, or Higher

get.summary: Gets active move for the specified customer

204.description: No active move for this customer

get.summary: Gets active contact (move or sales coordinator) for the specified move
